# https://example.org/arpo#affiliatedInstitution
<https://example.org/arpo#affiliatedInstitution> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://example.org/arpo#affiliatedInstitution> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://example.org/arpo#AffiliationRecord> .
<https://example.org/arpo#affiliatedInstitution> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://example.org/arpo#Institution> .
<https://example.org/arpo#affiliatedInstitution> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The institution named in an affiliation record." .
<https://example.org/arpo#affiliatedInstitution> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "affiliated institution" .
# 
# https://example.org/arpo#cites
<https://example.org/arpo#cites> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://example.org/arpo#cites> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#IrreflexiveProperty> .
