<https://example.org/arpo#cites> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://example.org/arpo#Publication> .
<https://example.org/arpo#cites> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Relates a publication to another publication it cites." .
