<https://example.org/arpo#hasAffiliation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has affiliation" .
# 
# https://example.org/arpo#hasAffiliationRecord
<https://example.org/arpo#hasAffiliationRecord> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
